<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Internship Application Deadline Alert</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #7c3aed; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
    .content { background: #f7fafc; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #7c3aed; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 15px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #718096; font-size: 12px; }
    .deadline-box { background: #fef3c7; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; margin: 15px 0; }
    .internship-card { background: white; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; }
    .company-name { color: #7c3aed; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Internship Deadline Alert</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{name}},</p>

      <div class="deadline-box">
        <strong>Application Deadline:</strong> Only <strong>{{daysLeft}} days</strong> left to apply!
      </div>

      <div class="internship-card">
        <p class="company-name">{{companyName}}</p>
        <h2>{{internshipTitle}}</h2>
        <p><strong>Deadline:</strong> {{deadline}}</p>
      </div>

      <p>Don't miss this opportunity! This internship matches your profile and could be a great addition to your career.</p>

      <p>
        <a href="{{applyUrl}}" class="button">Apply Now</a>
      </p>

      <p>Remember:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Review the internship requirements carefully</li>
        <li>Prepare your resume and cover letter</li>
        <li>Submit your application before the deadline</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Best of luck with your application!</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>College Management System</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated notification. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
      <p>You're receiving this because you match the eligibility criteria for this internship.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
